=== July ===
* July 15, the [[Government of Hungary|government]] introduced a state [[monopoly]] on [[retail]] [[tobacco]] sales. So-called National Tobacco Shops throughout [[Hungary]] became the only places where people could purchase cigarettes.<ref>http://theorangefiles.hu/state-monopoly-on-the-retail-sale-of-tobacco-2/</ref>
==Deaths== * June 19 – [[Gyula Horn]], politician, [[Prime Minister of Hungary]] (1994–1998), (b. 1932)
