ra]] || [[Kryštof (band)|Kryštof]] |- | 2016 || [[Thom Artway]] || [[Lenny (singer)|Lenny]] || [[Jelen (band)|Jelen]] |}
==History== *1991: originally formed as '''Annual Czechoslovak Music Awards''' (''Výroční československé hudební ceny'') *1992-1995: renamed to '''Gramy''' (''Gramy'') *1996: renamed to '''Czech Gramy''' (''Česká Gramy'') *1997: renamed to '''Music Academy Awards''' (''Ceny Hudební akademie'') *1998-2000: renamed to '''Academy of Popular Music Awards''' (''Ceny Akademie populární hudby'') *2001-2002: renamed to '''Angel Awards''' (''Ceny Anděl'') *2003-2007: subtitled as '''Angel Allianz Awards''' (''Ceny Anděl Allianz'') *2008–present: '''Angel Awards''' (''Ceny Anděl'')
