The '''Embassy of Ivory Coast''' in [[London]] is the [[diplomatic mission]] of [[Ivory Coast]] in the [[United Kingdom]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/263519/LDL_December_2013.pdf |title=The London Diplomatic List |date=13 December 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131211155353/https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/263519/LDL_December_2013.pdf |archivedate=2013-12-11 |df= }}</ref> The Ivory Coast also maintain a Commercial & Economic Section (Commodities) named " The Permanent Representation of Cote d'Ivoire to International Commodity Organizations" located at 33 Cavendish Square in Central London.

