'''Fria Airport''' {{airport codes|FIG|GUFA}} is an airport serving [[Fria]], a town and [[Prefectures of Guinea |prefecture]] in the [[Boke Region]] of the [[Republic of Guinea]]. The airport is on the southeast side of Fria.
