'''Nicole Lisa Gaelebale''' (born April 22, 1993) is a [[Botswana]] beauty queen. She was crowned Miss Global Botswana 2012. She represented [[Botswana]] at [[Miss Earth 2014]]. In 2015, she won second place and was crowned First Princess of Botswana. she also won [[Miss Botswana|Miss World Botswana 2017]] and represented [[Botswana]] at [[Miss World 2017]].<ref>{{cite web |last=Mathala |first=Sharon |title=Seneo Mabengano Crowned Miss Botswana 2015/2016 |date=2 October 2015 |website=Mmegi Online |url=http://www.mmegi.bw/index.php?aid=54525&dir=2015/october/02 |access-date=September 17, 2017 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20170917114601/http://www.mmegi.bw/index.php?aid=54525&dir=2015/october/02 |archive-date=17 September 2017 |dead-url=no |df= }}</ref> She was the 1st ever and only beauty queen in history to join the same international pageant twice, having represented the Botswana in Miss Earth 2014.

